data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 3506 Emory Drive in the heart of Holiday, Florida! This updated and well-maintained residence is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and a host of desirable features, this property is a rare find. Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting living space that seamlessly flows from room to room. The interior has been tastefully updated in 2018, boasting modern finishes that enhance the overall appeal of the home. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and appliances that make cooking a joy. The bedrooms are thoughtfully designed to provide a serene retreat, with ample natural light and well-designed storage solutions. The bathroom is a spa-like oasis, offering a relaxing environment to unwind after a long day. One of the standout features of this home is the expansive screened back porch. This versatile space is perfect for entertaining guests, enjoying al fresco dining, or simply unwinding while taking in the beautiful Florida weather. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends and family in this delightful outdoor haven. NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED. Don't miss the opportunity to make 3506 Emory Drive your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort this property has to offer. Welcome home!
